<li><a href="/wiki/Lashon_hara" title="Lashon hara">Not to embarrass others</a> — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0319.htm#17">Lev. 19:17</a></li>
<li>Not to <a href="/wiki/Oppress" class="mw-redirect" title="Oppress">oppress</a> the weak — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0222.htm#21">Ex. 22:21</a></li>
