<li><a href="/wiki/Torah_study" title="Torah study">To learn Torah</a> — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0506.htm#7">Deut. 6:7</a></li>
<li>To honor <a href="/wiki/Rabbi" title="Rabbi">those who teach and know Torah</a> — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0319.htm#32">Lev. 19:32</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Idolatry_in_Judaism" title="Idolatry in Judaism">Not to inquire into idolatry</a> — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0319.htm#4">Lev. 19:4</a></li>
