<li><a href="/wiki/Blasphemy" title="Blasphemy">Not to blaspheme</a> — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0222.htm#27">Ex. 22:27</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Idolatry_in_Judaism" title="Idolatry in Judaism">Not to worship idols in the manner they are worshiped</a> — Standard-&gt;<a class="external text" href="http://tools.wmflabs.org/bibleversefinder2/index.php?book=Exodus&amp;verse=20:6–20:6&amp;src=tlt">Ex. 20:6</a> Yemenite-&gt;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0220.htm#5">Ex. 20:5</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Idolatry_in_Judaism" title="Idolatry in Judaism">Not to worship idols</a> in the four ways we worship God — Standard-&gt;<a class="external text" href="http://tools.wmflabs.org/bibleversefinder2/index.php?book=Exodus&amp;verse=20:6–20:6&amp;src=tlt">Ex. 20:6</a> Yemenite-&gt;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0220.htm#5">Ex. 20:5</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Idolatry_in_Judaism" title="Idolatry in Judaism">Not to make an idol for yourself</a> — Standard-&gt;<a class="external text" href="http://tools.wmflabs.org/bibleversefinder2/index.php?book=Exodus&amp;verse=20:5–20:5&amp;src=tlt">Ex. 20:5</a> Yemenite-&gt;<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0220.htm#4">Ex. 20:4</a></li>
