<li>Not to eat the meat of minor sacrifices before sprinkling the blood — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0512.htm#17">Deut. 12:17</a></li>
<li>To bring meal offerings as prescribed in the Torah — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0302.htm#1">Lev. 2:1</a></li>
<li>Not to put oil on the meal offerings of wrongdoers — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0305.htm#11">Lev. 5:11</a></li>
<li>Not to put frankincense on the meal offerings of wrongdoers — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0303.htm#11">Lev. 3:11</a></li>
