<li>The Kohanim must eat the remains of the meal offerings — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0306.htm#9">Lev. 6:9</a></li>
<li>To bring all avowed and freewill offerings to the Temple on the first subsequent festival — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0512.htm#5">Deut. 12:5-6</a></li>
