<li>Not to offer any sacrifices outside the courtyard — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0512.htm#13">Deut. 12:13</a></li>
<li>To offer two lambs every day — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0428.htm#3">Num. 28:3</a></li>
