<li>The <a href="/wiki/Tzaraath" title="Tzaraath">metzora</a> must not remove his signs of impurity — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0524.htm#8">Deut. 24:8</a></li>
