<li>Observe the laws of impurity caused by <a href="/wiki/Childbirth" title="Childbirth">childbirth</a> — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0312.htm#2">Lev. 12:2</a></li>
<li>Observe the laws of impurity caused by a woman's <a href="/wiki/Zavah" title="Zavah">running issue</a> — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0315.htm#25">Lev. 15:25</a></li>
<li>Observe the laws of impurity caused by a man's <a href="/wiki/Zav" title="Zav">running issue</a> (irregular <a href="/wiki/Ejaculation" title="Ejaculation">ejaculation</a> of infected <a href="/wiki/Semen" title="Semen">semen</a>) — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0315.htm#3">Lev. 15:3</a></li>
<li>Observe the laws of impurity caused by a dead beast — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0311.htm#39">Lev. 11:39</a></li>
<li>Observe the laws of impurity caused by the eight shratzim (insects) — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0311.htm#29">Lev. 11:29</a></li>
<li>Observe the laws of impurity of a seminal emission (regular ejaculation, with normal <a href="/wiki/Semen" title="Semen">semen</a>) — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0315.htm#16">Lev. 15:16</a></li>
<li>Observe the laws of impurity concerning liquid and solid foods — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0311.htm#34">Lev. 11:34</a></li>
<li>Every impure person must immerse himself in a <a href="/wiki/Mikvah" class="mw-redirect" title="Mikvah">Mikvah</a> to become pure — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0315.htm#16">Lev. 15:16</a></li>
<li>The court must judge the <a href="/wiki/Damages" title="Damages">damages</a> incurred by a goring ox — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0221.htm#28">Ex. 21:28</a></li>
