<li>The court must judge the damages incurred by a pit — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0221.htm#33">Ex. 21:33</a></li>
<li>The court must judge the damages incurred by fire — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0222.htm#5">Ex. 22:5</a></li>
<li>Not to steal money stealthily — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0319.htm#11">Lev. 19:11</a></li>
<li>The court must implement punitive measures against the thief — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0221.htm#37">Ex. 21:37</a></li>
<li>Each individual must ensure that his scales and weights are accurate — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0319.htm#36">Lev. 19:36</a></li>
<li>Not to commit injustice with <a href="/wiki/Weighing_scale" title="Weighing scale">scales</a> and <a href="/wiki/Weight" title="Weight">weights</a> — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0319.htm#35">Lev. 19:35</a></li>
<li>Not to possess inaccurate scales and weights even if they are not for use — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0525.htm#13">Deut. 25:13</a></li>
<li>Not to move a <a href="/wiki/Boundary_marker" title="Boundary marker">boundary marker</a> to steal someone's property — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0519.htm#14">Deut. 19:14</a></li>
