<li><a href="/wiki/Canaan" title="Canaan">Canaanite</a> slaves must work forever unless injured in one of their limbs — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0325.htm#46">Lev. 25:46</a></li>
