<li>Return the collateral to the debtor when needed — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0524.htm#13">Deut. 24:13</a></li>
<li>Not to delay its return when needed — <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.mechon-mamre.org/p/pt/pt0524.htm#12">Deut. 24:12</a></li>
