<li id="cite_note-2"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-2">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">As stated by the <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.jewishvirtuallibrary.org/jsource/Judaism/mitzvot.html">Jewish Virtual Library</a>: "There is also complete agreement that these 613 <i>mitzvot</i> can be broken down into 248 positive <i>mitzvot</i> (one for each bone and organ of the male body) and 365 negative <i>mitzvot</i> (one for each day of the solar year)."</span></li>
